     I            DS
     I                                        1   8 W@DATE
     I                                        1   4 W@YY
     I                                        5   6 W@MM
     I                                        7   8 W@DD
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           P@YY    4
     C                     PARM           P@MM    2
     C                     PARM           P@DD    2
     C                     PARM           P@DATE  8
      *
     C                     MOVE P@YY      W@YY
     C                     MOVE P@MM      W@MM
     C                     MOVE P@DD      W@DD
      *
     C                     MOVE W@DATE    P@DATE
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
      *
